The men of Nigeria Security and Civil Defense Corps (NSCDC)Â  command Ilorin Kwara State has arrested a Man for Stealing water pumping machine in Ilorin,National Daily learnt.
The incident happened at about 1am Tegidini compound Adeta Ilorin when the suspect was caught while removing a bore hole water pump machine.
He was beaten by the community and handed over to the NSCDC for investigation.